<h2 class="bold font-l">Lupin the 3rd</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Jigen and Goemon decide to find out which weapon is more effective: a gun or a sword. </p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="alt-titles section section-fact">
<h3>
<strong>Alternative Title(s):</strong>
<span>Guns Versus Swords</span>, <span>Swords Vs Guns</span>, <span>Swords Versus Guns</span> </h3>
</div>
